text: École de management de Normandie is an European higher studies establishment. The school is in 5 places, in Paris, in Le Havre, in Caen, in Oxford and in Dublin. It is has been created in 1871.EM Normandie EM Normandie is specialist in the fields of economics, social sciences and management. ==References== == Further reading == * EM Normandie website Category:Education in France Category:Le Havre
